DefaultEvent.Description:
There is, in fact, a corpse within: utterly dead, unremarkable except for a slight bulge at the breastbone. Its skin is pale and cold. It's not clear what he died of.

Even as you watch, the skin seems to tighten further. When you return, an hour later, the corpse is already half-decayed, into something like a pile of withered leaves. So much for that.
DefaultEvent.Name: Not unexpected

ChildBranches.Name: Crack the seal and see what's inside.

Description: Is it, in fact, a coffin?
Name: Soothe & Cooper Long-Box
